{"tid":1817432,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"內地專家：針對武漢肺炎病原體研發新藥物需時數年","createTime":"2020-01-09T05:37:03.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-09T06:53:51.000Z","uid":130626,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"ee2ab6bbf99c20ca1df428c651dd14e0b37a36c9","tid":1817432,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-09T05:37:03.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】武漢不明肺炎病原體初步判定為新型冠狀病毒，內地專家組指，研發新藥物需時數年，下一步需要結合流行病學調查和臨床表現等進行研究。<br />\n<br />\n央視報道，實驗室在周二驗出一種新型冠狀病毒，獲得該病毒的全基因序列。經核酸檢測，驗出有15宗呈陽性結果，並在其中一名病人的樣本分離出該病毒，病毒呈典型冠狀病毒形態。<br />\n<br />\n專家指，下一步需要結合病原研究、流行病學調查和臨床表現進行專家研判，要從病人身上發現病原的核酸、基因組和抗體證據，可在短期內完成，而病毒分離和致病性鑑定等研究需要數周時間。針對新發病原體的特效藥物和疫苗研發，則需要數年時間。<br />\n<br />\n冠狀病毒除人類以外，還可以感染豬、牛及蝙蝠等多種哺乳類動物及鳥類。目前已知人類冠狀病毒有六種，其中四種致病性較低，另外兩種包括嚴重急性呼吸綜合症冠狀病毒，即「SARS」，及中東呼吸綜合症冠狀病毒，即「MERS」，可引起嚴重呼吸系統疾病。<br />\n<br />\n今次的新型冠狀病毒不同於已發現的人類冠狀病毒，暫未有命名，要進一步研究。<br />\n<br />\n武漢市衞健委日前公布，當地不明原因肺炎個案增至59宗，8名患者已出院。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E5%85%A7%E5%9C%B0%E5%B0%88%E5%AE%B6-%E9%87%9D%E5%B0%8D%E6%AD%A6%E6%BC%A2%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E%E7%97%85%E5%8E%9F%E9%AB%94%E7%A0%94%E7%99%BC%E6%96%B0%E8%97%A5%E7%89%A9%E9%9C%80%E6%99%82%E6%95%B8%E5%B9%B4-020637714.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E5%2585%25A7%25E5%259C%25B0%25E5%25B0%2588%25E5%25AE%25B6-%25E9%2587%259D%25E5%25B0%258D%25E6%25AD%25A6%25E6%25BC%25A2%25E8%2582%25BA%25E7%2582%258E%25E7%2597%2585%25E5%258E%259F%25E9%25AB%2594%25E7%25A0%2594%25E7%2599%25BC%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2597%25A5%25E7%2589%25A9%25E9%259C%2580%25E6%2599%2582%25E6%2595%25B8%25E5%25B9%25B4-020637714.html&d=y5xLblNGdgzQkswvdzbF0%2FY%2F4yEwT0EAZMYNsJUacQ0%3D&h=c6edc664\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E5%85%A7%E5%9C%B0%E5%B0%88%E5%AE%B6-%E9%87%9D%E5%B0%8D%E6%AD%A6%E6%BC%A2%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E%E7%97%85%E5%8E%9F%E9%AB%94%E7%A0%94%E7%99%BC%E6%96%B0%E8%97%A5%E7%89%A9%E9%9C%80%E6%99%82%E6%95%B8%E5%B9%B4-020637714.html</a>"},{"pid":"5044ffb11fed2071afb8a30da3539a95c57bdc9c","tid":1817432,"uid":277186,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-09T05:38:44.000Z","msg":"最好既新年禮物<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />中國大瘟疫 2020 GDP望10都黎啦"},{"pid":"fa2dc05e2f57d9a018cffd69c74e5507109fb2a0","tid":1817432,"uid":130626,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-09T06:49:21.000Z","msg":"到左研究成功，到時啲人都死晒啦"},{"pid":"a44e7a3e2bcd2c045b4bc8c62fd36223bd9c47ec","tid":1817432,"uid":163704,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-09T06:50:08.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n[全港最大的Fact Check平台-非食店篇]集合超過400間各地區各行業的良心店<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1817378\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1817378</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"8a4baac6eb69f65769882e6388e1bdfeac8c74e0","tid":1817432,"uid":48670,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"fa2dc05e2f57d9a018cffd69c74e5507109fb2a0","tid":1817432,"uid":130626,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-09T06:49:21.000Z","msg":"到左研究成功，到時啲人都死晒啦"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-09T06:50:57.000Z","msg":"咁咪成功2020全面踏入小康<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f2353159242fb3b1450c0f88583b3ae09bb0776e","tid":1817432,"uid":311004,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-09T06:53:23.000Z","msg":"直接叫武漢呼吸綜合症<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb26354e81f07a8585114e2bd6f15ef4ff8e2999","tid":1817432,"uid":311004,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8a4baac6eb69f65769882e6388e1bdfeac8c74e0","tid":1817432,"uid":48670,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"fa2dc05e2f57d9a018cffd69c74e5507109fb2a0","tid":1817432,"uid":130626,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-09T06:49:21.000Z","msg":"到左研究成功，到時啲人都死晒啦"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-09T06:50:57.000Z","msg":"咁咪成功2020全面踏入小康<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\